{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"jason.log","author":"Jaesung Lee","siteUrl":"https://jason0853.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"jason0853/gatsby-blog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"HFzVClS"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"26d2b5bf-e84c-57f9-bd00-1a86aba804e9","excerpt":"이번에 드디어 react 기반인 로 블로그를 마이그레이션하게 되었다. 콘텐츠도 그대로 이전할 생각도 있었지만 다시 공부해서 올리는게 개인적으로 도움이 될 것 같았다. 그래서 어떤 포스팅을 먼저 올릴까 고민해보았는데 역시 내가 제일 좋아하는 로…리액트리액트는 페이스북에서 나온 UI 라이브러리이며 리액트 공식 홈페이지를 보면…","html":"<p>이번에 드디어 react 기반인 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby</code>로 블로그를 마이그레이션하게 되었다. 콘텐츠도 그대로 이전할 생각도 있었지만 다시 공부해서 올리는게 개인적으로 도움이 될 것 같았다. 그래서 어떤 포스팅을 먼저 올릴까 고민해보았는데 역시 내가 제일 좋아하는 <code class=\"language-text\">react</code>로…</p>\n<h2 id=\"리액트\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%95%A1%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"리액트 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리액트</h2>\n<p>리액트는 페이스북에서 나온 UI 라이브러리이며 <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/\">리액트 공식 홈페이지</a>를 보면 3가지가 메인에 나온다. <code class=\"language-text\">Declarative</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Component-Based</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Learn Once, Write Anywhere</code>, 즉, 다시말해서 ‘선언적이며, 컴포넌트를 기반으로 둔 개발이며, 한 번 배워서 어디서든지 쓸 수 있다.‘라고 정의를 내린다.</p>\n<p>자, 그럼 바로 리액트 프로젝트를 생성해주는 cli 툴을 이용해서 연습해보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> react-test <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">cd</span> react-test\n$ npx create-react-app <span class=\"token keyword\">.</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> start</code></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/8e724/react-basic-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 60.902777777777786%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"react basic 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/b9e4f/react-basic-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/cf440/react-basic-1.png 148w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/d2d38/react-basic-1.png 295w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/b9e4f/react-basic-1.png 590w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/f9b6a/react-basic-1.png 885w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/2d849/react-basic-1.png 1180w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/bbefa/react-basic-1.png 1770w,\n/static/a8ce9f8cda1502693d966f8f303e7d5c/8e724/react-basic-1.png 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>이제부터 간단한 counter 예제를 통해 react의 가장 중요한 개념인 <code class=\"language-text\">setState</code> 함수에 대해 알아보자!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Counter.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleIncrease</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">prevState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> prevState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>number <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> ✅\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    <span class=\"token comment\">// this.state.number = this.state.number + 1 ❌</span></span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// console.log(this.state.number);</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"counter\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>You clicked <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> times<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>handleIncrease<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Counter</code></pre></div>\n<p>리액트에서 상태값(state)을 업데이트 하기 위해선 <code class=\"language-text\">setState</code> 함수를 통해서 업데이트를 해야한다. 만약 state를 직접 변경한다면 화면에 변경된 값은 렌더링되지 않을 것이다. 그 이유는 리액트에선 이전 상태값과 기존 상태값을 비교해서 화면에 리렌더링하는 구조로 설계되어있다. 그 비교를 하기 위해서 무조건 setState 함수를 호출해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'counter'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  user<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Jason'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">35</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>만약 위와 같이 state가 되어 있다면 어떤식으로 user의 age 값을 변경해야할까?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ❌ wrong way</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">prevState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">  user<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span>    age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> prevState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>age <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ✅ right way</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">prevState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  user<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>prevState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> prevState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>age <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>첫번째 방식처럼 이전 user 상태값을 변경해버리면 user의 객체는 변경되어버린다. 참고로 setState는 <strong>shollow copy</strong>, 즉 얕은 복사만 할 수 있다. 그래서 깊은 복사는 ES6 문법인 <code class=\"language-text\">spread operator</code>를 이용하여 이전 객체를 copy한 뒤 age 값을 변경해야한다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"리액트 기초 다지기","date":"May 23, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/react/리액트-기초-다지기/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react/리액트-테스트/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"리액트 테스트","category":"react"}},"next":null}}